# Verification Gate

Rules:
- Never claim “done” unless verification passes.
- Prefer one “verify” script if repo has it.
- Otherwise run repo scripts in order: lint → typecheck → tests → build.
- If infra doesn’t exist, propose adding it (but do not add deps without approval).
